{"id": "art-122", "label": "Art. 122", "title": "Art. 122", "slug": "art-122", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 122 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1815933735\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1260\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1815933735\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Munca suplimentar&#259; se compenseaz&#259; prin ore\nlibere pl&#259;tite în urm&#259;toarele 90 de zile calendaristice dup&#259;\nefectuarea acesteia.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)În aceste condi&#355;ii\nsalariatul beneficiaz&#259; de salariul corespunz&#259;tor pentru orele\nprestate peste programul normal de lucru.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)În perioadele de reducere a\nactivit&#259;&#355;ii angajatorul are posibilitatea de a acorda zile libere\npl&#259;tite din care pot fi compensate orele suplimentare ce vor fi prestate\nîn urm&#259;toarele 12 luni.</span></p>"}